title: NDC Melbourne
abstract:
NDC Melbourne is a 3-day developers conference taking place at the Melbourne Convention and Exhibition Centre from 29 April - 1 May 2025.

There will be awesome workshops and presentations by some of the world's leading developer trainers and speakers.

See the Agenda here: https://ndcmelbourne.com/agenda
